<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.9.6">
<l>collā toḻiya killē ṉaṟinta collil nummaṭiyār</l>
<l>ellā rōṭu mokka veṇṇi yiruntī raṭiyēṉai</l>
<l>nallā raṟivīr tīyā raṟivīr namakkiv vulakattil</l>
<l>ellā maṟivī rītē yaṟiyī rinta ḷūrīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I cannot leave without speaking, in words which are understood.</l>
<l>You keep considering me like all of your servants.</l>
<l>You who knows good people, you knows bad people,</l>
<l rend="indent">you who knows everything in this world,</l>
<l>You do not know this about us, you of Intaḷūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
